data.description: Well maintained, move-in ready home in Madison – 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath mid-century ranch with original hardwoods (recently refinished). Freshly painted interior. Windows have been replaced. 1.29 acre lot with woods to the rear of the home. River view from the front porch (when leaves are down).  1-car attached garage and carport with 2 additional parking spaces. Convenient to Madison retail, restaurants, and parks.
